						<p>This records a tax-free gift of land made after purchase from the <hi rend="italic">Ūrār</hi> of Poyyaraiśūr in Kīḻāṉmūr-nāḍu for burning two lamps in the temple of Mūlasthāṉattu-Perumāṉaḍigaḷ of Śrīyāṟṟuttaḷi at Tirumuḍiyūr by a certain Kōvaḍiuḍaiyāṉ of Brahmapurinallūr in Maḻa-nāḍu.</p>						

